Double Punch/Counter Punch (Punch)/Manterror/Injector/Bumblebee:



In Counter Punch's voice, he yelled into his comm. unit to the Preds.  "It's 
Counter Punch, the four Maximals are on the move!  Two are airborne, I 
repeat, two are airborne!  The Alliance forces are in the rear.  I'm moving 
in to attack, Counter Punch over."

Punch ran after his Alliance brethren, weapon raised.

---

Double Punch saw something in the sky, Manterror stepping up next to him.

"Should we fire on i--"

Manterror was interrupted, the two Predacons recieving Counter Punch's 
transmission.

"YES!" Double Punch yelled, going into his cloaked mode, heading off for the 
two Maximals on the ground.

Manterror laughed, heading quickly to get in firing range of the flying 
Maximals.

---

Bumblebee and Injector, in the air flying together, spotted Prowl, holding 
Iron Raptor.

"I think...we should welcome them to our airspace." Bumblebee chuckled.

"This...isn't our airspace."

"It was a joke!" Bumblebee countered.

"Uh huh...how about we just slag them and bring their heads back as prizes?"

"Why?"

"Good point.  Let's just slag 'em!"

"YEAH!"

The two pulled out a stinger missile launcher each, blasting off at full 
speed, recieving Counter Punch's transmission.

Bumblebee raised his launcher, firing off two rockets at Iron Raptor's torso, 
who was in Prowl's arms.

Injector fired two stinger missiles off at Prowl's left hand, knowing he 
would probably just miss and hit the big guy in his hands, but that was ok.
